OL,3,CWoman raped at Newcastle Town Moor in
OL,4,Cdaylight attack
OL,6,FA woman in her 40s has been raped in
OL,7,Fthe middle of the day as police hunt
OL,8,Fthe man responsible.
OL,10,FThe attack happened between 2:15pm and
OL,11,F3:15pm on Tuesday (23 June) at the
OL,12,FTown Moor in Newcastle.
OL,14,FOfficers say the woman was raped by a
OL,15,Fman unknown to her after they met a
OL,16,Fshort time earlier on a footbridge
OL,17,Ffrom Claremont Road in the Spital
OL,18,FTongues area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
