OL,3,CWoman raped at Newcastle Town Moor in
OL,4,Cdaylight attack
OL,6,FThe man is described as white, aged in
OL,7,Fhis mid-30s, approximately 5ft 8in
OL,8,Ftall, of muscular build with short
OL,9,Fdark hair with grey flecks.
OL,11,FHe is believed to be wearing black
OL,12,Fjogging pants and a white t-shirt and
OL,13,Fhad been riding a pedal bike.
OL,15,FAnyone with information, CCTV or
OL,16,Fdashcam footage is asked to contact
OL,17,FNorthumbria Police.
